--------------------Routing RIP Static -------------------------
	-> Routing with other network adding those n/w isn't this network.
-> configure ip of each router 
************** command *************
1. select router 
2. enable ( press enter )
3. config terminal ( press enter )
4. interface gigabiethernet 0/0 , 0/1 ,0/2 ( press enter )
5. ip address 10.0.0.3_255.0.0.0 ( press enter )
6. no shutdown ( enter )
7. do wr .
******************* routing commond **********************
1. enable ( enter )
2. config terminal ( enter )
3. router rip ( enter )
4. network 30.0.0.0_255.0.0.0_20.0.0.2 < gateway > (enter)
   network 40.0.0.0_255.0.0.0_20.0.0.2 < gateway > (enter)
   network 50.0.0.0_255.0.0.0_20.0.0.2 < gateway > (enter)
5.do wr ( enter ) 
___________________________________________________________
   
--------------------- Routing Rip Dynamic -----------------
	-> Routing with self network and configure routing .
-> configure ip of each router 
************** command *************
1. select router 
2. enable ( press enter )
3. config terminal ( press enter )
4. interface gigabiethernet 0/0 , 0/1 ,0/2 ( press enter )
5. ip address 10.0.0.3_255.0.0.0 ( press enter )
6. no shutdown ( enter )
7. do wr .
******************* routing commond **********************
-> perform on selected network .

1. enable ( enter )
2. config terminal ( enter )
3. router rip ( enter )
4. network 10.0.0.0 (enter)
   network 20.0.0.0 (enter)
   network 30.0.0.0 (enter)
5. do wr ( enter )
________________________________________________________________